show.description: This is a  romantic drama following the classic premise of love across socio-economic divides. The story centers on a wealthy heir who, tired of being valued only for his riches, goes undercover as a common man. In this guise, he meets a beautiful heiress burdened by an arranged marriage driven by family expectations. What begins as a pragmatic contract evolves into genuine affection, as both discover authenticity and kindness beneath their privileged facades
